  "instructions": [
    "Cut the double-rise bread into 1-inch cubes and toast until golden brown.",
    "In a blender or food processor, puree the toasted bread until it resembles crumbs.",
    "In a medium saucepan, heat the ghee over medium heat until it starts to foam.",
    "Add the fish sauce, salted egg, and black sesame seeds to the ghee and stir until combined.",
    "Add the honey and kalamansi juice to the ghee mixture and stir until dissolved.",
    "Add the heavy cream to the ghee mixture and stir until combined.",
    "Fold in the toasted bread crumbs, crushed plantain chips, and coconut shavings.",
    "Pour the mixture into individual serving cups or glasses.",
    "Top with crushed pandan leaves, a drizzle of honey, and a sprinkle of black sesame seeds.",
    "Place in the freezer for at least 30 minutes to set.",
    "Serve cold and enjoy!"
  ],
